featured_reviews.review_id:
Such a great masjid
Its a large masjid
I often doing salah in town jumua masjid.
Khathib and the surroundings are great
Clean water for dringing and wudu
Now they are preparing space for womens to make salah
At the time of fasting everyone will open there fast with delicious food items.
Well appreciated committy members are behind the success of this juma masjid.
Each year the masjid is developing
Vast space help us to gain spiritual energy
Free from vehicles sound outside.
So nice
Great masjid
Keep going 
Mashallah...

Save yourself from innovators
Preaches pure Tauheed and trying to stick on to the  Sunnah of the Holy Prophet (PBUH).  However the formal Friday sermon (Jumu'a Khutba) delivered in Malayalam. A place where your spirituality attains tranquility and peace. A place where you are blessed with many other people who have a common goal to be better humans. A place where you do good to get good.people go here in search of peace, prosperity, positivity, purity so on and so forth. Their intentions vary from wide array of emotions, such as, from worldly gains to afterworld gains. To wash away their sins, to ask for forgiveness, peace, health wealth.. Or, simply, to feel closeness to the divine authority....
jzk llhu khyran
